						<p>Ubu Roi is still in "should" rather'n "did", and I imagine I'll have to revisit all this after that and I guess Strauss are properly digested.</p>
<p>You ever think about making an "essential" category, btw (have I asked this fifty times already?)?</p>
						</li>

										<li id="comment-164417" class="adminbody"><div class="adminhead"><img alt='Mircea Popescu`s avatar' src='http://trilema.com/avatar.png' class='avatar avatar-32 photo' height='32' width='32' />								<div class="commentcount">6</div>
